node.text:
Having focused primarily on lighting for the past few years, renowned international designer @leebroom debuts new furniture and accessories with The Penthouse Collection. Comprising the White Street Sofa, Tribeca Tables, Musico Table and Chairs and Fulcrum Candlesticks, the new collection was created for Lee Broom’s New York penthouse which completed in Spring 2021. Each piece is inspired by the design details of the Tribeca interior and the architecture of its surroundings. The full collection is now available to order from Lee Broom.⁣
•⁣
